 ok‚Üêtest_config(folder name);z;config;userfile;ns;files;export;getj5;fn;link;here;opts
‚çù Verify that the system is using configuration according to the spex

 getj5‚Üê{‚éïJSON‚çÝ'Dialect' 'JSON5'‚ä¢‚äÉ‚éïNGET ‚çµ}

 SetConfig'' ‚çù Clear user config file
 3 ‚éïNDELETE Retry‚ä¢folder
 3 ‚éïMKDIR Retry‚ä¢folder
 ‚éïEX name
