 z‚Üê'(flatten:0)'‚éïSE.Link.Export name export         ‚çù flatten is meaningless in the context of Export
 z‚Üê‚éïSE.Link.Configure export'flatten:1'             ‚çù Test setting option in named file
 assert'1‚àä''flatten: ''‚ç∑z'                          ‚çù flatten:0 is default so was not stored in config
 config‚Üêgetj5 export,'/.linkconfig'
 assert'1‚â°config.Settings.caseCode' ‚çù caseCode should be picked up from re-exported link

 z‚Üê‚éïSE.Link.Break name
 ‚éïEX name

